long_description: The 32GB Delkin Devices Class 10 SD card is optimized for use in compatible action cams, smartphones, digital cameras, GPS and other handheld devices. Memory card offers reliable storage for media-rich applications, including high-definition photos, MP3s and even full 1080p videos. SD card provides minimal transfer rates up to 24MB per second. Class 10 SD.
